# AGENTS.md — shop-api

Instructions for coding agents working in this repository.

## Project

TypeScript Node HTTP API for a fictional shop.

## Before you search

1. Read this file.
2. Skim `README.md` and folder names under `src/`.
3. Prefer reading likely files directly over repo-wide grep.

## Layout

- `src/server.ts` — likely main entry (confirm with package.json scripts)
- `src/auth/` — authentication
- `src/catalog/` — product APIs
- `src/billing/` — invoices
- `src/webhooks/` — outbound webhooks
- `src/lib/` — shared utilities

## Conventions

- Use TypeScript strict mode.
- Small, reviewable diffs.
- Do not run mass replace scripts across the whole tree without explicit approval.

## Tests

No test suite in this benchmark fixture.
